data.description: Looking for "peace & quiet" on your own fully fenced 4.32 acre mini ranch? This property is it! Only 8 miles from Kingman off paved road. 360 degree views of mountains, desert and Kingman city lights. Terrific area for star gazing!     Perfection plus in this ground set home with concrete perimeter. Retro fit has been installed. 2 car detached garage with epoxy flooring. Garage workshop with cabinets galore and a free standing wood burning stove.    There is spacious room for RV parking for your friend and family visits. Full RV hook-ups. Mature landscaping.    Property has a unique Gazebo with windows that can be removed for year round enjoyment. Separate chain link dog run. In-ground fire pit with seating area.    Immaculate move-in ready three bedroom, 2 bath home. All new appliances, paint and flooring. Third bedroom has double door, which would be perfect for office or in-home student schooling. This is a must see property! You will absolutely love it!  Come take a look.
